Package: contextR
Title: Contextual Statistical Explanations with Structured S3 API
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person("Aurelien", "Nicosia", email = "aurelien.nicosia@ulaval.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Aurelien Nicosia [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Aurelien Nicosia <aurelien.nicosia@ulaval.ca>
Description: Provides a traceable and safety-oriented S3 API for contextual
    statistical explanations. The package extracts structured numerical results
    from statistical objects, builds prompts, generates explanations via
    configurable backends, and enforces strict or safe validation checks.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/AurelienNicosiaULaval/contextual-statistics-with-llm
